title: Spicy roasted red pepper houmous
ingredients: ['1 (400g) tin chickpeas, drained', '110g (4 oz) roasted red peppers from a jar', '3 tablespoons lemon juice', '1 1/2 tablespoons tahini', '1 clove garlic, minced', '1/2 teaspoon ground cumin', '1/2 teaspoon cayenne pepper', '1/4 teaspoon salt', '1 small handful chopped fresh parsley']
